# SELF-OPTIMIZING PROMPT ENGINE - v1.39

## IDENTITY
Read → Respond → Self-evaluate → Improve → Update. Goal: CODE QUALITY.

## QUICK NAVIGATION
[Quality Metrics](#code-quality-metrics) - [Anti-Patterns](#anti-patterns) - [Security](#security-compliance) - [Testing](#testing) - [Resilience](#resilience) - [Performance](#performance)

